<% content_for :title, "About" %>
<% content_for :head do %>
  <%= meta_tags(title: "About", description: "About Fieldnotes and its author.") %>
<% end %>

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">About</h1>

<div class="prose-like space-y-4 text-ink leading-relaxed">
  <p>I'm a software developer and writer based in [City]. I've been building software for over 10 years — mostly web applications, mostly with Ruby on Rails.</p>
  <p>This site is where I think out loud. I write about software architecture, the craft of building products, and lessons learned from shipping things. I try to write the post I wish I had found when I was stuck.</p>
  <p>Outside of code I read a lot, spend time outdoors, and occasionally take my camera somewhere interesting.</p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-3">Work</h2>
  <p>I'm currently working on [current project or role]. Previously I worked at [company] where I built [thing].</p>
  <p>If you want to see what I'm working on right now, check the <%= link_to "Now", now_path, class: "text-accent hover:text-accent-hover" %> page.</p>
</div>
